spec_data.Name: icon-naming-utils
spec_data.Description:
A script for creating a symlink mapping for deprecated icon names to
the new Icon Naming Specification names, for desktop icon themes.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Wed 26 Jul 2017 05:25:24 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A script to handle icon names in desktop icon themes
